---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { useTranslations } from "../../../i18n";

const lang = "en";
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<Layout title={t.legal.privacy.pageTitle} theme="light">
    <main
        class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-brand-dark lg:prose-lg"
    >
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-8 text-surface">
            {t.legal.privacy.title}
        </h1>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-8 rounded-r">
            <p class="text-blue-800 font-medium">
                <strong>ℹ️ Note:</strong> This privacy policy is subject to Spanish
                and European data protection law. The official binding version is
                the <a href="/legal/privacidad" class="underline"
                    >Spanish version</a
                >.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p class="lead">
            The objective of the Privacy and Data Protection Policy of C.I.E.
            FUERTEVENTURA, S.L. is to protect information on the internet and
            the data that the user may enter on the website, in compliance with
            applicable legislation (GDPR and Spanish LOPD).
        </p>

        <p>
            The use and navigation of the website, as well as the subscription
            of any forms contained therein, will imply acceptance by the user of
            this Privacy and Data Protection Policy.
        </p>

        <hr class="border-gray-200 my-8" />

        <h3>Use and Processing of Personal Data</h3>
        <p>
            In compliance with the applicable regulations, we inform you that
            the data provided, as well as data derived from your navigation, may
            be stored in files owned by C.I.E. FUERTEVENTURA, S.L., who will
            access them solely for the purpose of attending to your request,
            managing the requested service and maintaining the relationship
            established in the forms you subscribe to.
        </p>

        <h3>Security Measures</h3>
        <p>
            C.I.E. FUERTEVENTURA, S.L. has implemented the necessary technical
            and organizational security measures to guarantee the security of
            your personal data and prevent its alteration, loss and unauthorized
            treatment and/or access, taking into account the state of
            technology, the nature of the stored data and the risks to which
            they are exposed.
        </p>

        <h3>
            Exercise of Rights: Access, Rectification, Cancellation and
            Opposition
        </h3>
        <p>
            Individuals who have provided their data to C.I.E. FUERTEVENTURA,
            S.L. may contact us to exercise their rights of access,
            rectification, cancellation and opposition regarding the data
            incorporated in our files.
        </p>
        <p>
            The interested party may exercise their rights through written
            communication addressed to C.I.E. FUERTEVENTURA, S.L. at the
            following address: Avda. de la Constitución, 3 floor 1 door 4, Gran
            Tarajal 35620 LAS PALMAS, or via email at
            <a href="mailto:cieasesoria@gmail.com">cieasesoria@gmail.com</a>
        </p>

        <h3>Minors</h3>
        <p>
            The services provided by this website are not directed at minors
            under 14 years of age, so data from these individuals should not be
            provided.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
